;◇イベント05・ホテルに再宿泊
*hotel_5

; 翌朝・ホテルのロビー
@eval exp='game.curChara = o.テオ.getRoomMates()[0]'
@wait time=1000
@bg f=0037
@mu f=guild
[texton w=1]
After checking out of the hotel, we waited outside for Sandra to return.[k]
@fg c=サンドラ f=01
[サンドラ v=vn058 f=01]「Sorry for the wait.」[k]
[テオ e=現在の装備 f=01]「Sandra!」[k]
Sandra came back. She's as carefree as ever.[k]
[サンドラ v=vn059 f=01]「How was it? Did you have fun last night?」[k]
[キャラ e=現在の装備 f=25]「... (Kyaa)」[k]
[テオ f=33]「U-umm, well...」[k]
Apparently, Sandra thinks we had a relationship.[k]
[テオ f=05]「More importantly, how did yesterday's undercover investigation go?」[k]
@fg c=サンドラ f=07
[サンドラ v=vn060 f=07]「Yes, I finally caught the enemy red-handed!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Really?!」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn061 f=08]「That hotel has a secret passageway underground for members only, and they arrange prostitution there. If we catch them in the act, we can expose the reality of prostitution.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn062 f=07]「Let's sneak in there tonight. Once you're ready for battle, meet us all in front of the hotel again. Okay?」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Understood.」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w1

; 夕方・ホテル前
@bg f=0038
[texton w=1]
That evening.[k]
Our party gathered again near the hotel and devised a plan centered around Sandra.[k]
@fg c=サンドラ f=08
[サンドラ v=vn063 f=08]「The secret passage can only be accessed from inside the hotel, so tonight, just like yesterday, pretend to be a normal couple when you check in, and then wait in your room.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn064 f=08]「Meet at the designated place at midnight. Got it?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Understood.」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05

; ホテル内
[texton w=0]
Sandra infiltrated the hotel again. The rest of us paired up like yesterday and checked in the same way.[k]
Then, I stayed in my room and waited for the meeting time to come.[k]
[textoff]
@fa

[iscript]
game.hour = "night";
o.ライナス.events.remove(0);
game.hotelView.openRoamingMap(o.ホテル・クイーン);
game.hotelView.sleepButton.visible = false;
game.innActionCount = 1;
for(var i = 0; i < game.hotelView.visMarkers.count; i++)
{
	if(! game.hotelView.visMarkers[i].visible) continue;
	game.hotelView.visMarkers[i].selectable = false;
}
game.hotelView.getRoomFromRoomName("従業員通路").clear();
[endscript]

@addeventbtn map=ホテル・クイーン label=隠し通路_1 name=隠し通路 img=sandra x=900 y=200
[hoteloff]


