;◇イベント01・依頼を受ける
*barn_1

; マルティナの酒場
[texton]
[依頼人 f=grosjean_00]「Oh, hello... Are you the one who accepted my request? My name is Grojean. I am a knight.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「As the title suggests, I would like you to investigate whether my wife Eleanor is having an affair.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「My wife is a very cute younger wife, and we've been married for two years... I thought we were getting along well, but lately my wife's attitude has been strange.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「Suspicious, I pretended to go to work and secretly observed my wife at home.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「...Then, I saw my wife entering a shed in a field near our house with a man I didn't know!」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「I confronted my wife... She said that he was just helping out in the fields. She said she loved me and would never betray me.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「It's true that my wife is very devoted and fulfills her role as a wife properly. She treats me more kindly than before... So I want to trust her.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「...But I just can't shake this uneasy feeling! For some reason, I can't calm down!」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「So I decided to thoroughly investigate my wife. If nothing came of it, I would finally be able to rest easy.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「Adventurers, would you please investigate my wife? Once you have thoroughly investigated her, I think I can accept the results, whatever they may be.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「...I know it's a selfish request. I don't want to doubt my beloved wife either. But as things stand, I don't have the confidence to continue living with her...」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「My wife usually works in the fields near our home. The fields are located northwest of Emile Plain, just outside the south gate of this town. Thank you very much.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「I don't think you can judge the situation after just one visit, so please observe the situation for a few days and report back to me with the results.」[k]
[textoff]
[baroff]


