;◇イベント03・依頼人に報告
*barn_3

; マルティナの酒場
[texton]
I returned to the tavern and reported the results of my investigation to the client.[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「Is that so... So my wife was cheating on me after all...」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「To be honest, I am shocked, but that's clearly how things are... I will have to consider divorcing my wife. I am grateful for your efforts this time.」[k]
The client looked completely dejected. There were no words of comfort left to say.[k]
@se f=door1
[name n=Eleanor f=elenor_02]「Oh, it's you. What are you doing here? I thought you were away on a knight expedition and wouldn't be back for a while?」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_01]「Eleanor! Where have you been all this time?」[k]
[name n=Eleanor f=elenor_01]「What's wrong? I was just doing my usual farm work.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_01]「Don't play dumb...! I know you're cheating on me with another man!」[k]
[name n=Eleanor f=elenor_01]「What are you talking about? I only love you.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_01]「I know everything! I know what you're doing in that shed!」[k]
[name n=Eleanor f=elenor_03]「...Oh, you knew about it. Well, then there's no point in saying anything else.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_00]「Guh...! You finally confessed!」[k]
[name n=Eleanor f=elenor_02]「...It's your fault. You're rarely home because of your work with the knights, and even when you do come home... I don't know how to put it, but you're so indifferent, you never satisfy me.」[k]
[name n=Eleanor f=elenor_01]「In that respect, Pat is wonderful... He's energetic, youthful, and passionate... He's completely different from you. He's there for me whenever I need him...」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_01]「Guh... How indecent! I'm divorcing you!」[k]
[マルティナ f=02]「What's wrong with you two? Don't make a scene in my bar.」[k]
[name n=Eleanor f=elenor_02]「Ah... Martina.」[k]
[マルティナ f=02]「What happened? Eleanor, please tell me.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_01]「This woman was cheating on me behind my back!」[k]
[name n=Eleanor f=elenor_02]「Sure, I cheated, but it's his fault in the first place. He neglected me, and he's weak down there, so he can't satisfy me at all...」[k]
[マルティナ f=01]「...Eleanor, you're such a hopeless case. I lost my husband a few years ago, so I understand your frustration, but even so, cheating is not right.」[k]
[name n=Grosjean f=grosjean_01]「Divorce! Divorce! I will never forgive you!」[k]
It seems that this situation won't be easily resolved. It's not my place to get involved in other people's problems, so I'd better leave.[k]
[textoff]
