[texton]
Next morning.[k]
I recall last night's proposal and become lost in thought.[k]
[テオ e=通常 f=06]「...」[k]
Yesterday, I finally got engaged to my wife...[k]
She happily agreed to marry me, and my heart was filled with joy and relief.[k]
...I had been anxious. What if she'd turned me down?[k]
Anyway, now all that's left is to get married to my wife.[k]
...For marriage, you have to have a wedding ceremony at a [b]church[/b], having prepared two [b]wedding rings[/b] that are exactly the same.[k]
And above all, we need to resolve the issue with the demon Murmur and sever our ties with Blue.[k]
We can't let Blue get involved in our married life, and anyway, with Murmur potentially attacking at any moment, this is no time to be thinking about marriage.[k]
It's been tough, but I want to get married as soon as possible for her sake. It would be cruel to keep her waiting.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
Murmur hasn't been sighted since our last encounter.[k]
There's no doubt that she's somewhere in this world, but she hasn't approached us again.[k]
It is precisely because we do not know when we she'll attack that we are working with Blue.[k]
In other words, as long as that devil is somewhere in this world, I cannot leave Blue.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
With the power to exorcise demons, it is possible to defeat Murmur. I have defeated her once before, so it is definitely possible.[k]
All that's left is to find out where she is.[k]
