[サンドラ v=vn072 f=07]「Hey, check out this quest!」[k]
Saying that, Sandra shows me what appears to be a flyer she brought with her.[k]
It was a copy of a quest notice from a tavern. I read through it.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
The request stated that a troop of trolls was attacking human settlements.[k]
Apparently, the trolls who lived in the cave settlement have emerged from the cave in large numbers and are attacking the surrounding towns and villages one after another.[k]
The request suggests that the security forces alone cannot handle the situation, so they want adventurers to lend a hand. In other words, they are encouraging adventurers to participate in the troll extermination operation.[k]
