[テオ f=05]「Y-yes...」[k]
Reading further, there was information about a certain person who was leading the trolls.[k]
[テオ f=05]「...A little devil girl is leading the trolls...?」[k]
So the trolls have a leader. That makes sense, since alone, trolls are too stupid to systematically search for and attack villages.[k]
But... this little devil girl, could it be...?![k]
[サンドラ v=vn074 f=08]「Hey, surely it's that girl?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
A little devil girl who would do something like this could surely only be...[k]
[テオ f=05]「...I'll ask the party to join me on this quest! Will you come with us, Sandra?」[k]
