Eventually... her entire body turned to ash and crumbled away without a trace.[k]
[テオ f=12]「Did we do it...?」[k]
All that remained was ash. It was blown away by the wind and scattered into the mist.[k]
And then she disappeared completely from this world. This time, we had finally destroyed the devil Murmur.[k]
[サンドラ v=vn079 f=02]「...Looks like it's over.」[k]
[マックス f=03]「Yeaaaah!」[k]
Max lets out a cry of joy! We defeated that detestable devil![k]
This time, we destroyed her physical form. She will never return. I have finally put an end to this battle.[k]

[if exp='HUM && game.curChara != game.wife'][リム v=vh077 f=03]「You did it! Captain!」[k][endif]
[if exp='ELF && game.curChara != game.wife'][クレア v=ve078 f=01]「Good job, Captain!」[k][endif]
[if exp='DWA && game.curChara != game.wife'][フレデリカ v=vd077 f=03]「You did it～!」[k][endif]
