[texton w=1]

; 婚約者のヒロインが静かに話しかけてくる
[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh078 f=22]「Captain...」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve079 f=22]「Captain...」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg066 f=22]「Captain...」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs080 f=22]「Captain...」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=05]「[ヒロイン]...!」[k]
With sparkling eyes, [ヒロイン] approaches me.[k]
I am moved as I watch my fiancée's smile.[k]
We finally achieved our goal...! We accomplished our goal of defeating the devil Murmur...![k]

[   if exp='isHUM'][リム v=vh079 f=22]「Captain, now we can...」[k]
[elsif exp='isELF'][クレア v=ve080 f=22]「Captain, now we can...」[k]
[elsif exp='isGNO'][ミューズ v=vg067 f=22]「Captain, now we can...」[k]
[elsif exp='isSYL'][マルエット v=vs081 f=22]「Captain, now we can...」[k]
[endif]

[テオ f=02]「...Yes, we're going to be together.」[k]
That's right, once we defeat Murmur, we'll get married. That's what we decided together.[k]
The time has finally come to fulfill our promise.[k]
