@fg l=ブルー e=通常 f=06 b
@fg r=サンドラ f=01
[texton w=1]
[サンドラ v=vn080 f=01]「This is where we part ways. Captain.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Thank you very much for everything. It's thanks to you that I have been able to make it this far.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn081 f=03]「It was fun. Let's go on another adventure together if we get the chance.」[k]
[テオ f=01]「Yes!」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Blue...」[k]
[ブルー f=06]「...」[k]
Blue is still the worst kind of person. I feel angry that the gods would give such a person the power to exorcise demons.[k]
...However, it is true that Blue helped us defeat Murmur. He is a truly unpleasant individual, but he kept his word at the very least.[k]
[テオ f=06]「I would like to express my gratitude for keeping our agreement. There is no doubt that it was thanks to you that we were able to defeat the devil.」[k]
[ブルー f=01]「Hmph... I got what I wanted, so I have no complaints.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「We've been through a lot together, but I'm grateful. This is goodbye. I hope that from now on, you will walk the path of a proper adventurer.」[k]
[ブルー f=05]「Don't talk so condescendingly. I'll carry on doing whatever I want.」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn082 f=01]「See you later.」[k]
@cl
Blue left with Sandra.[k]
[textoff]

@se f=period
@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.ブルー)'
@eval exp='game.guest.removeMember(o.サンドラ)'
@notice text="<y>Blue and Sandra left the party."

[texton w=0]
[マックス f=09]「Phew, we finally got rid of Blue. Just having him around makes me nervous～」[k]
Max says with a look of relief on his face. Everyone else in the party also looks relieved.[k]
In any case, this is a turning point. With this, our party's activities will return to normal.[k]
We don't have to worry about the devil or Blue anymore.[k]

