;◇主人公ホテルイベント・結婚後
*hotel_wife_1

; ラブホテルの一室
@saveon
@mu f=affair
@se f=door1
@bgf f=0004
@wait time=1000
@fg l=テオ f=10 b
@fg r=ヒロイン f=05
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
[ヒロイン f=05]「...」[k]
After checking in, I entered a room at the love hotel with [ヒロイン].[k]
Pink walls and carpet. A heart-shaped double bed. You couldn't mistake it for anything other than a love hotel.[k]
@se f=door1
@fgf l=テオ f=05
[従業員]「Excuse me, excuse me.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Aaa...」[k]
Suddenly, an employee suddenly entered the room unannounced.[k]
[従業員]「We offer a free laundry service. Please put your clothes in this basket. We will wash them and return them to you by tomorrow morning.」[k]
[ヒロイン f=06]「...」[k]
A laundry service...?[k]
It may be convenient, but we brought weapons and other items with us in case something happened. I'd rather not leave our belongings with others.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Uh... That's fine...」[k]
[従業員]「We are sorry, but this service is mandatory for all guests staying at this hotel.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What...?」[k]
You're saying laundry service is mandatory? What on earth is going on?[k]
[従業員 f=01]「You see, we have had problems in the past with guests staying at this hotel, including vandalism and murder...」[k]
[従業員 f=01]「To prevent any problems, we ask our customers to leave all their luggage, including what they are wearing.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「I see...」[k]
[従業員]「In return, we will wash the clothes you leave with us. Thank you very much for your cooperation.」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
If that's the case, we have no choice but to accept...[k]
We're here to conduct an undercover investigation of this hotel. I'm a little reluctant to check in all our luggage...[k]
However, disobeying the employees will be regarded with suspicion. It would be counterproductive to be refused accommodation.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Okay, I'll leave my clothes and luggage with you.」[k]
[従業員]「Thank you for your cooperation! Please them in this basket. Please wear this instead.」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w1
@bg f=0004 b
@fg l=テオ e=バスタオル f=26 b
@fg r=ヒロイン e=バスタオル f=25
[texton]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[ヒロイン f=25]「...」[k]
After depositing all of our clothes, [ヒロイン] and I were only clad in towels.[k]
This was all the employee offered us to wear.[k]
[テオ f=25]「Um... You didn't have anything else to wear?」[k]
[従業員]「Sorry, we wanted to provide bathrobes, but unfortunately we are out of stock...」[k]
[テオ f=26]「Oh no...」[k]
[従業員]「...Isn't it fine? Given what you are both here for, after all.」[k]
The employee then smiles a little condescendingly.[k]
[テオ f=26]「...」[k]
...This is one of those places where if you stand out too much, people may become suspicious. Ostensibly, [ヒロイン] and I are just an ordinary couple who came to stay at a love hotel.[k]
[テオ f=26]「I understand. Please take care of the laundry.」[k]
[従業員]「Well, enjoy yourselves.」[k]
@se f=door1
∗slam∗[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[ヒロイン f=25]「...」[k]
Going to a love hotel with my wife feels... kind of strange.[k]
[テオ f=02]「...Should we just go about our day as usual, [ヒロイン]?」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05
[texton]
[if exp='game.wife.equip.hip == o.鋼鉄の貞操帯（ブルーの所持品）']
	After that, [ヒロイン] and I quietly spent a night alone together for the first time in ages.[k]
	I would have liked to have sex with her, but since she was wearing Blue's chastity belt, I had no choice but to give up.[k]
[else]
	After that, [ヒロイン] and I sought each other's bodies as usual.[k]
	Perhaps it was the lewd atmosphere of the love hotel that made our sex more exciting than usual.[k]
	@eval exp='game.curChara = game.wife'
	@recordsex guy=テオ sex=&'intrandom(2, 3)' orgasm=&'intrandom(1, 3)'
[endif]
[textoff]
@fa
@w05
